    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good overall condition. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, reflecting regular servicing throughout its life. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear, and the exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you may find a few small stone chips upon close inspection. All electronics and features are fully functional. This is a reliable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
