    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, and the exterior shows several deep dents and peeling clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tears and persistent staining. It is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts, as it is not currently reliable for daily driving.",
